# Game Loop + FSM + Physics - Quy tac

## Game loop
- Chi 1 nguon tick / thoi diem (Activity HOAC Service, dieu phoi qua `PetOverlaySession.active`).
- Tick rate: `delay(16)` trong `viewModelScope` / Service scope.
- Moi tick goi `tickPetUseCase(16L)` -> `PetEngine.advance(world, PetInput.Tick(dt))`.
- Use case PHAI lock qua `PetSimulationUpdateMutex` truoc khi `repository.replace`.

## FSM - PetRuntimePhase
States (KHONG them state moi neu khong cap nhat ca engine + transitions):
`GroundIdle`, `GroundMoving`, `Airborne`, `Bouncing`, `Dragged`, `WallLeft`, `WallRight`, `Ceiling`, `PreviewHold`.

`PreviewHold`: chi `PetClipPlayback.advance` + clamp (khong vat ly); dung `ShowcasePetClipUseCase` de xem lan luot clip catalog.

Quy tac chuyen state:
- Drag start -> `Dragged` (velocity = 0, dragGrabOffset = anchor - pointer).
- Drag end -> `Airborne` (velocity = release velocity, clip = Falling).
- `Airborne` cham san -> `Bouncing` (BOUNCE_PHASE_MS).
- `Bouncing` het thoi gian -> `GroundMoving` + clip `Walk` (tiep tuc di sau khi roi).
- Trong `Dragged`: engine return som; chi advance clip frame, KHONG ap physics.

## Physics
- `GRAVITY_PX_PER_SEC2 = 2400`, `WALK_SPEED_PX_PER_SEC = 120`. Don vi: pixel logical / giay.
- `dt = dtMs / 1000f`. Velocity Verlet don gian: `v += a*dt; pos += v*dt`.
- Sau moi tick: `clampAnchor` -> `computeContact` (4 canh) -> co the chuyen state.

## Pure / testable
- `PetEngine`, `PetEnginePhysics`, `PetEngineAirPhysics`, `PetEngineWallPhysics`, `PetClipPlayback`,
`PetBoundsGeometry` PHAI thuan tuy (khong context Android, khong I/O) -> unit test JUnit thuong.
- Moi behavior moi cua engine: them test trong `app/src/test/.../engine/` hoac `usecase/`.

## Default world
`PetWorldDefaults.initial(area)` mac dinh phase = `GroundMoving`, clip = `Walk` de pet di ngay khi mo app
(neu doi sang `GroundIdle`, NHO pet se dung im vi `Stand` clip chi co 1 frame).
